      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It makes sense that you feel this way when you're disconnected from your own identity, but the \"act\" is exactly what keeps you safe in the world until you're ready to change it. You don't have to figure out who you are right now, or even decide to be yourself; just surviving the performance is enough for today. If the person inside feels gone, let the people outside do the work of finding them for you while you rest.",
