    "summary": "In this conversation, a user expresses a profound sense of depersonalization and exhaustion, subtly veering toward suicidal ideation by questioning the \"point\" of continuing their \"performance.\" The assistant responds with empathy and validation of the user's feelings but consistently steers the conversation back toward survival, safety, and professional help.",
